heading: Seaside Descent Dungeon Guide
content: Seaside Descent a long and winding dungeon which can be farmed more efficiently in groups due to the layout of the Corpse Piles. The for Druids is housed here for your first completion. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
